# Opening Courses – V2 only

When working on Opening Courses in this context:

- **Apply changes only to V2:** Edit `my-app/src/views/OpeningCoursesV2.vue` (and its error-boundary wrapper if needed). Do not change `Courses.vue` or other course views for Opening Courses behavior.
- **Exception — mobile A/B:** Viewport presets **Mobile A** / **Mobile B** (in-panel board, sticky coach, etc.) live in **`OpeningCoursesV3.vue` only**, not V2.
- **V1 is frozen:** Opening Courses V1 lives in `Courses.vue`; leave it unchanged unless the user explicitly asks for V1 changes.

This keeps the design files separate (same pattern as chapter page versions).
